{
  "stem": "6130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, my-- my father appeared at home [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before his second child was born.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was-- well, he-- he just was very upset and very angry, and ordered him out of the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he-- these are the people who wouldn't let me in when I went in, and called the genedarmes for me, that I am digging for treasures.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyhow, my father got kind of sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He really wasn't sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was in his 80s.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was a strong, healthy man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But he said-- when the-- the word came around that sooner or later, we will be transported from the ghetto-- he said, I am not ever leaving the house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They will have to take me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one night, he just fell into a coma, and he died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But before that, when we knew he was sick, I don't remember how, but we let word go to my youngest brother, who was in the labor camp not too far from Kaposvar.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a labor camp there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he came before my father died, a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The way he-- he escaped from the labor camp-- because he wasn't allowed to leave-- he went on a train, spent all that time in the toilet, and he got into the ghetto jumping the fence, and there he was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had a doctor with us also who was living in my parents' house, and he said, oh, if just Mr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Vago could have a little milk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
